125
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,919
You've become quite a talker.

126
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,440
I pay my respects to you, Father.

127
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,440
I pay my respects to Your Majesty.

128
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,279
Thank you, Your Majesty.

129
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,720
Qingcheng, come here.

130
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:55,559
Father, I am not a filial child.

131
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,840
I haven't taken good care of you.

132
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,720
It's my fault.

133
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:01,559
I know

134
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,720
