135
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:07,200
The Crown Prince hasn't matured.

136
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:08,879
You've worked hard.

137
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:13,960
It seems

138
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:16,240
