139
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:18,279
It's troublesome.

140
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,240
Who is he?

141
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:27,320
Father, he is Chu Xiaoran.

142
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:29,559
I invited him here to treat you.

143
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,600
