154
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:16,600
Rest assured, I'm trained in medicine.

155
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,919
I have the basic knowledge.

156
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,480
In that case,

157
00:11:30,879 --> 00:11:33,759
